434
00:25:24,510 --> 00:25:25,840
You can't fall for that.

435
00:25:28,060 --> 00:25:29,160
Lu Zheng and Yizhong

436
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,890
were arrested at the same time.

437
00:25:31,210 --> 00:25:32,140
Yizhong

438
00:25:32,380 --> 00:25:34,580
has now been escorted back to your home,

439
00:25:35,110 --> 00:25:36,630
