446
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:49,350
Xixing,

447
00:25:51,210 --> 00:25:52,940
since Wu Zixu built Suzhou City

448
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:55,300
2,500 years ago,

449
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,840
among the eight major families in Suzhou,

450
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:58,670
Lu and Gu have always been the leading families.

451
00:25:58,670 --> 00:26:01,070
We rise or fall together.

452
00:26:02,600 --> 00:26:04,620
You should know what you're doing, right?

453
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:05,300
Of course.

454
00:26:06,870 --> 00:26:09,170
If you dare to take office

455
00:26:09,190 --> 00:26:10,920
as the magistrate of Wu County,

456
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:12,660
don't blame me, Lu,

457
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:14,270
